---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';

// You'll need to add an actual avatar image to your assets
// import avatarImage from '@/assets/avatar-tanaka.jpg';
const avatarImage = "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1303300587958616065/Glrp1DHj_400x400.jpg";
---

<section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white dark:from-gray-900 dark:to-gray-800">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">
        <div class="md:w-1/3 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 p-8 flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="relative w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4">
              <Image 
                src={avatarImage} 
                alt="アバター" 
                class="rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-lg"
                width={128}
                height={128}
              />
              <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 bg-green-400 rounded-full w-6 h-6 border-2 border-white"></div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">堂前 紀郎</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-200">MG-DX 代表取締役</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-2/3 p-8 flex flex-col justify-center">
          <Icon name="mdi:format-quote-open" class="w-12 h-12 text-blue-500 mb-4" />
          <blockquote class="text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            分野や職種問わず何事も「<strong>最新サービスはとにかく使い倒した人が勝つ</strong>」のがこの業界の<strong>20数年前から変わらない絶対ルール</strong>です。
          </blockquote>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-end">
            <Icon name="mdi:twitter" class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400 mr-2" />
            <a href="#" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">@tanaka_pm</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>